SUMMARY:Rising from the Dust: The Legacy of Michelle Materre exhibit
DESCRIPTION:Curated by archivists Sarah Petras and Dan Hassoun\, this exh
 ibit showcases posters\, collages\, photos\, and realia relating to the c
 areer of pioneering film distributor Michelle Materre\, including origina
 l materials from the first release of Daughters of the Dust! Stop by the 
 BFCA office to get a look at this exhibit\, which will stay up for the re
 mainder of the 2025-2026 academic year.&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Curated by archivists Sarah Petras and 
