X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  In celebration of the 100th anniversary of Pau
 lin S. Vieyra's birth\, the BFCA presents <em>TOTAL AFRICAN CINEMA</em>\,
  an exhibition honoring the pioneering filmmaker\, critic\, &amp\; histor
 ian who helped shape African cinema.\n</p>
